Dialogue: 5,0:00:01.67,0:00:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What about these?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:04.61,0:00:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna, those are weeds.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:08.25,0:00:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you wanna use those for a bridal bouquet.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:12.04,0:00:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're so cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.75,0:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't there any fancier flowers like roses or moth orchids growing around here?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.00,0:00:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, henbits!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.63,0:00:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I really be helping Aka{-chan} with getting married?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:25.04,0:00:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like hibernation isn't an option anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:28.14,0:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess that's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.15,0:00:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bad person.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.90,0:00:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.01,0:00:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Hikari to be saved, too...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:39.72,0:00:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't want him to go into hibernation.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.32,0:00:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is, I don't want to be separated from Aka{-chan}.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.23,0:00:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:49.02,0:00:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't want to be separated from Hikari either?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:52.26,0:00:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that make me a bad person?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that makes two of us!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.94,0:00:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.23,0:01:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,want to be apart from Kaname either!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.94,0:01:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally evil.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.20,0:01:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not evil!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:04.22,0:01:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm—
Dialogue: 5,0:01:06.73,0:01:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.79,0:01:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky! I'm totally more evil!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:16.21,0:01:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Miuna{-san}...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:17.27,0:01:20.34,Alternative,,0,0,0,,A pervert!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.23,0:01:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna! Cram those flowers in his face!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
