Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.47,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.67,0:03:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you were Aka{-chan} and Hikari's dad.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.86,0:03:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your fingers are super hairy, and you had a pervy aura, so...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.91,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.69,0:03:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell Aka{-chan} and Hikari to go to sleep in the ocean?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's noble! You're such a good girl, Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.19,0:03:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No one really knows what will happen even if we do hibernate.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.28,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The danger facing the surface is still far off into the future.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.55,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So for all we know, both Akari and Hikari might be happier living on the surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... That's right!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.40,0:04:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, mister!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, not "mister."
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.02,0:04:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aka{-chan}'s going to be your mom, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.49,0:04:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.98,0:04:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.02,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Hikari and the others should be out of school soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse us.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.12,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Please excuse us.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grandpa"...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, where are we meeting up today?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.24,0:04:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The fishery cooperative.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.32,0:04:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Go ahead without me.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.12,0:04:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I got him to help out the wardrobe crew.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's with Chisaki and Manaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.10,0:04:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little nerve-racking having those two take the train into the city on their own.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.11,Naru Nami Shine,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\frx0\fry349\c&HDF9283&\org(1078,332)\pos(678.429,-9.714)}Thrift Store
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this looks good.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little out of our budget.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.14,0:05:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.72,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the cut's a little too wide.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you from the ocean, by any chance?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.45,0:05:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.92,0:05:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're looking for a kimono,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,how about this one?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit dull.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.62,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tsumugu{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.75,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like I heard.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:38.99,0:05:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This was sold to us by a lady who lived in the ocean.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.21,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's apparently made to reflect your Ena's shine.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.79,0:05:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a special discount, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.13,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a stroke of luck, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.42,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The hem is a little short, so I'll have to adjust it later.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.70,0:05:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you two come with me for a bit?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one sec.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who that is?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure that's Tsumugu{-kun}'s mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.88,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take this. For Grandpa.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.00,0:06:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you in good health.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.33,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Grandpa doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as usual.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.17,0:06:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, would you like to get something to eat?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.54,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm here with my friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.71,0:06:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.31,0:07:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Miuna made me realize something.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew of the danger that was coming to the surface,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.20,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so you opposed my marriage to Itaru{-san} for my own good, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.57,0:07:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet I had no idea. I acted like a child.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.91,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized something too after I saw her.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.19,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.13,0:07:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Had there been some way your mother didn't have to leave us forever,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably would have chosen that.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.03,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the Boatdrift Ceremony and the wedding coming along?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.57,0:07:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari and the others are even taking care of my wardrobe for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.12,0:07:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all so perfect that I can't treat him like a kid anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.65,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.43,0:07:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the Boatdrift Ceremony and the beginning of your hibernation{split if necessary} fall on the same day.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.58,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Mom can watch me get married from the ocean.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.36,0:08:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me say it.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be the only chance I'll get.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.27,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When Mom died, you were the one who had it the hardest.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.47,0:08:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, you watched over us, never letting those emotions show.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.11,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After Mom died,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.13,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you made soup for us for the first time.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget how it tasted.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.13,0:08:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The giant, uneven pieces of carrots and daikon...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.83,0:08:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was clumsy, yet warm and kind.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.32,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.71,0:09:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The love that you gave us...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to give that love to Miuna and Itaru{-san} as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.91,0:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being such a selfish, difficult daughter to the very end.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.43,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything you've done for me over the years.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.04,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna wave this.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.74,0:09:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.74,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So that the Wooden Maiden can head straight for the sea god without getting lost.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So that everything ends up where it belongs.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Without getting lost...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything ends up where it belongs...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, hold it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it tight now.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.89,0:09:58.99,Alternative,,0,0,0,,So... heavy...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari{-kun}.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to wave one of the flags during the ceremony?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.98,0:10:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Would that be okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have the upper-body strength.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's too much for a kid.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not! Please let me do it!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.68,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you hold it like that, you'll get blisters.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.07,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hikari sure tries hard.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally asleep.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.49,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you sleep, too?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.63,0:10:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to stay awake when your Ena's so thick, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.29,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari's gone as far as stealing other people's lunches,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.63,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but apparently that's still not enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not just about food.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.49,0:10:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it just happens to all of you at certain times.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that okay with your mom?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.97,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I ended up using you as an excuse.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really want to talk to her.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.55,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I thought that I was the only one who was suffering.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.56,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone's going through a lot, and they're all in pain,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet they're all trying so hard.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.13,0:11:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I took it out on you and said some terrible things.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.82,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.53,0:11:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pathetic of me. It really was.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you decide on something?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.12,0:11:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear it in your voice.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.47,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Being too perceptive won't score you points with the girls, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.05,0:11:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back already?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember sitting down, and then it's all a blur.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.66,0:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka, your drool's shining on your face.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.93,0:12:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.81,0:12:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.66,0:12:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That flag's huge!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.57,0:12:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When did Hii{-kun} become a man?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.15,0:12:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing. Let's go.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got the kimono now, so it's almost done.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess things up.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're back.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sir...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.21,0:13:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Children's cells multiply a lot faster.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Their Ena thickened more quickly,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and they fell asleep before the day of hibernation.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.87,0:13:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the day of hibernation?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.02,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} will perform the appropriate ritual, and then they'll go into hibernation.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.78,0:13:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you guys will be hibernating before us.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.55,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.23,0:13:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like your Ena hasn't developed very much, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.51,0:13:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there they go.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.22,0:13:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter whose turn it was to do the Boatdrift Ceremony,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.24,0:13:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the songs were always our duty.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about crappy singing.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get from the Ena-less.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You should show them how it's done.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happens when we hibernate?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When you actually look at them...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.69,0:14:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...they look like they're dead, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you wanted to say, right, Manaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.17,0:14:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this takes me back.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.68,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.52,0:14:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, our heights!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.63,The Club of the Kettle,,0,0,0,,{\fsp1\fax-0.2\blur1.2\c&H503916&\frz12.52\move(640,158,639.97,-169.44,24,2485)\1a&H0F&}Hikari
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.63,The Club of the Kettle,,0,0,0,,{\fsp1\fax-0.2\blur1.2\c&H503916&\frz12.52\move(633,326,632.97,-1.44,24,2485)\1a&H11&}Kaname
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.63,The Club of the Kettle,,0,0,0,,{\fsp1\fax-0.2\blur1.2\c&H503916&\frz12.52\move(627,407,626.97,79.56,24,2485)\1a&H08&}Chisaki
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.63,The Club of the Kettle,,0,0,0,,{\fsp1\fax-0.2\blur1.2\c&H433113&\frz12.52\move(621,818,620.97,490.56,24,2485)}Manaka
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.69,0:14:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.63,0:14:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We recorded them at the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.30,0:14:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an old habit from grade school that just kind of stuck.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.09,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's mark our heights now.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find something for us to write with!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.82,0:14:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's check out the faculty room.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.98,0:14:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.19,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are amazing, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.02,0:15:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to tell you,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so maybe after this...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.01,0:15:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Found one.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.29,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was it?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.28,0:15:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you find anything?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe down, kids.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.86,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. This will be on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:24.65,Sakishima Akari,,0,0,0,,{\shad1\blur0.6\c&HE5E0C5&\4c&HDAD3AC&\b1\4a&H50&\1a&H50&\fscx80\fscy80\move(968,264,990,264,22,2942)\frz2.331}Thanks, Namiji Junior High
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you read your textbooks.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's mimicking {replace}Teach{Sensei}!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun} sounds just like him!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.94,0:15:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you're not my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:38.45,Sakishima Akari,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.05\shad1\blur0.6\c&HE5E0C5&\4c&HE5E0C5&\b1\4a&H50&\1a&H50&\frz359.1\fscx95\fscy95\pos(832,188.667)}T{*\c&HE4DFC3&\4c&HE4DFC3&}h{*\c&HE3DEC2&\4c&HE3DEC2&}a{*\c&HE2DDC1&\4c&HE2DDC1&}n{*\c&HE1DCC0&\4c&HE1DCC0&}k{*\c&HE0DBBF&\4c&HE0DBBF&}s{*\c&HDFDABE&\4c&HDFDABE&}, {*\c&HDDD8BB&\4c&HDDD8BB&}N{*\c&HDCD7BA&\4c&HDCD7BA&}a{*\c&HDBD6B9&\4c&HDBD6B9&}m{*\c&HDAD5B8&\4c&HDAD5B8&}i{*\c&HD9D4B7&\4c&HD9D4B7&}j{*\c&HD8D3B5&\4c&HD8D3B5&}i {*\c&HD6D1B3&\4c&HD6D1B3&}J{*\c&HD5D0B2&\4c&HD5D0B2&}u{*\c&HD4CFB1&\4c&HD4CFB1&}n{*\c&HD3CEB0&\4c&HD3CEB0&}i{*\c&HD2CDAE&\4c&HD2CDAE&}o{*\c&HD1CCAD&\4c&HD1CCAD&}r {*\c&HCFCAAB&\4c&HCFCAAB&}H{*\c&HCEC9AA&\4c&HCEC9AA&}i{*\c&HCDC8A9&\4c&HCDC8A9&}g{\c&HCDC7A8&\4c&HCDC7A8&}h
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Teach{Sensei}, I have a question.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.04,0:15:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Kaname{-kun}, what might it be?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Teach{Sensei} doesn't say that.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Righto.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what might it be?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.09,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about Manaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname, why would you do that?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just let things stay like this.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.78,0:15:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.80,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Ena keeps developing whether we eat or not.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we go to sleep,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.09,0:16:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't be sure we'll wake up together.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.90,0:16:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know that!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.72,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.41,0:16:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We may never see each other again.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even know if we'll wake up at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never again...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.31,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never again...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never again...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.07,0:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.79,0:16:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,love Manaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.34,0:16:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hii{-kun}...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.58,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Don't joke about that.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.76,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a joke.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you like Tsumugu, I...{so wait, Kaname loves Chisaki, Chisaki loves Hikari, Hikari loves Manaka, Manaka loves Tsumugu, Tsumugu... i imagine this is what korean dramas are like}{clearly tsumugu loves kaname. qed}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand any of that!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.64,0:17:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That was horrible, Kaname!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You went too far!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.59,0:17:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing the best I can, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.37,0:17:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run after her!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run after her!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, I...{suddenly underwater gravity strikes}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, I...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.82,0:18:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But... You like Manaka, so I couldn't say it.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't scared of rejection, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.05,0:18:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared that if I told you how I felt,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.84,0:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it would change everything between us.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.66,0:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so I thought, but that wasn't it either.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it out.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.42,0:18:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with the person you are now. The one who loves Manaka so much.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling you how I felt was enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm satisfied with that.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go run after Manaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.45,0:19:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,First you say not to run after her, and now you tell me the opposite.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about demanding.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.65,0:19:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just like you.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.59,0:19:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared of destroying our relationships.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But telling you how I felt was enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen to us?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will change.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so kind, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.77,0:19:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.17,0:19:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be kind.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have a beautiful heart.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.81,0:19:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As beautiful as the view of Shioshishio from here.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.08,0:20:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that I still need to put everything away.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.67,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll—
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.23,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, Mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.15,0:20:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Ena's gotten so thick.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.37,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The hibernation is coming up soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.32,0:20:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I... forgot something at school.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps, it's late.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.86,0:20:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that weird cough.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.94,0:20:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the ocean people go into hibernation,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we may not be able to get any more fish.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.77,0:20:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that happens...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.67,0:20:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take it easy and rest.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.87,0:21:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.21,0:21:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared. I don't understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where should I go?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.88,0:21:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where should I go
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.09,0:21:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here! Over here!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{he caught a waifu...}{lol, show pls}
