Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.95,0:23:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I always admired it.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:32.06,0:23:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:32.54,0:23:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the sea, beyond the sky...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:33.13,0:23:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You were crying.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:34.63,0:23:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surrounded by noise.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:35.26,0:23:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun that was so far, far away.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}, wave that flag!
